<H3> <TI>   Yeltsin Makes Administration Changes in Belgorod, Krasnodar </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Yeltsin Makes Administration Changes in Belgorod, Krasnodar </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   LD2006092694 Moscow Mayak Radio Network in Russian 0900 GMT 
20 Jun 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD2006092694 </F>
<F P=104>  Moscow Mayak Radio Network </F>
<F P=105>  Russian </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Boris Yeltsin has appointed Georgiy Golikov head of 
administration of the city of Belgorod for the period till the 
relevant local self-rule bodies are formed. This was reported 
today by the presidential press service. 
  By another decree he released Nikolay Yegorov from the post 
of head of administration of the Krasnodar Kray in connection 
with his assignment to another post. The press service gives no 
information as to who has been appoined instead of him. 

</TEXT>

