BFN 

  [Text] In order for the presidential edict on further 
improvement of land relations to be carried out, the Cabinet of 
Ministers endorsed the procedures of purchase and sale by legal 
entities and citizens of the Republic of Kazakhstan of the right 
to the lifelong inheritance and possession, use, or rent of land 
plots. The state committee of land relations and land use is 
