<F P=100> Tajikistan </F>
<H3> <TI>   Russian Guards Foil Border Incursion </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Russian Guards Foil Border Incursion </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   LD2006083394 Moscow ITAR-TASS in English 0808 GMT 20 Jun 94 </F>
<F P=103> LD2006083394 </F>
<F P=104>  Moscow ITAR-TASS </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

<F P=106> [Report by ITAR-TASS correspondent Galina Gridneva] </F>
  [Text] Dushanbe 20 June TASS -- Russia border guards foiled 
an attempt at an armed penetration of the territory of 
Tajikistan from Afghanistan by a small group of Tajik opposition 
in Shuroabad border sector guarded by the Moskovskiy Border 
Detachment on the night from Sunday to Monday. 
  The border gourds opened artillery fire on the crossing 
area, 
forcing the intruders to withdraw to the contiguous bank. Foe 
losses are unknown. There were no losses among Russian 
servicemen, military sources in Dushanbe told ITAR-TASS. 
  In all, over the past 48 hours, border guards thwarted six 
border crossing attempts. The situation remained relatively 
calm in the other sectors of the Tajik-Afghan border. 

</TEXT>

