<H3> <TI>   Official on Black Sea Cooperation Body </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Official on Black Sea Cooperation Body </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   LD2006093294 Kiev Radio Ukraine World Service in Ukrainian 
