<F P=103> LD2006205994 </F>
<F P=104>  Moscow 2x2 Television </F>
<F P=105>  Russian </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] The FRG Government has fulfilled its promise to 
grant Russia a favorable loan of 500 million German marks for 
the construction of housing for servicemen. A third of this sum 
has already been allocated previously, and Russia will receive 
the rest before the end of the year. Agreement on this was 
reached during the current visit to Germany by a delegation of 
the State Duma, led by its Speaker Ivan Rybkin, which ended on 
Sunday. 

</TEXT>

