<H3> <TI>   Cypriot House Delegation Meets Kozyrev </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Cypriot House Delegation Meets Kozyrev </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   NC2006152594 Nicosia Cyprus Broadcasting Corporation Radio 
Network in Greek 1500 GMT 20 Jun 94 </F>

<F P=103> NC2006152594 </F>
<F P=104>  Nicosia Cyprus Broadcasting Corporation Radio 
Network </F>

<F P=105>  Greek </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Russian Foreign Minister Andrey Kozyrev said that 
his country is interested in a just solution to the Cyprus issue 
and is studying the channeling of its efforts in this direction. 
  Kozyrev's statement was made today during a meeting with 
House of Representatives President Alexis Galanos and the 
members of the parliamentary delegation visiting Moscow. 
Galanos asked for Russia's support for convening an 
international conference, for an investigative visit to Cyprus 
by the UN Security Council and for the proposal on disarmament 
in Cyprus. Galanos noted that Russia can play a 
counterbalancing role on the Security Council. 

</TEXT>

