<H3> <TI>   Chernomyrdin, Other Republic Leaders Congratulate Masol </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Chernomyrdin, Other Republic Leaders Congratulate Masol </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   LD2006130094 Kiev Ukrayinske Radio First Program Network in 
Ukrainian 1100 GMT 20 Jun 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD2006130094 </F>
<F P=104>  Kiev Ukrayinske Radio First Program Network </F>
<F P=105>  Ukrainian </F>


<TEXT>
