<H3> <TI>   Denies Withdrawing Candidacy </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Denies Withdrawing Candidacy </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   LD2006103394 Moscow INTERFAX in English 1010 GMT 20 Jun 94 </F>
<F P=103> LD2006103394 </F>
<F P=104>  Moscow INTERFAX </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Ukrainian Parliament speaker and candidate to the 
presidential post Aleksandr Moroz has denied reports by 
Ostankino TV company that he may remove his candidacy and 
support Leonid Kravchuk. 
  "This is a canard of which I was informed last week," he 
told 
electors in Zaporozhye. 
  "I respect all candidates to the presidential post, but I 
have no comrades-in-arms among them," he said. 

</TEXT>

