<F P=103> LD2006164594 </F>
<F P=104>  Moscow ITAR-TASS </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Moscow June 20 TASS -- Russian President Boris 
Yeltsin signed several decrees on Monday appointing Aleksey 
Kazakov head of the Department for Work with Territories of the 
Russian Presidential Administration and Vladimir Varov head of 
the Federal Labour Inspectorate of the Russian Ministry of 
