<H3> <TI>   New Witnesses Summoned at Trial </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    New Witnesses Summoned at Trial </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   LD2106110994 Moscow ITAR-TASS in English 1050 GMT 21 Jun 94 </F>
