<H3> <TI>   Unprofitable Coal Mines To Be Closed Down </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Unprofitable Coal Mines To Be Closed Down </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   PM2106094394 Moscow IZVESTIYA in Russian 17 Jun 94 p 1 </F>
